1:1: COMMENT NOTE
1:7: STR_LIT "
    斯篇專演「循環」與「明斷」之妙用。
    借《張丘建算經》之「百錢買百雞」題，
    以驗多重迴圈、算術運算，並以多言列印之功也。
"
7:1: HERE_ARE i have
7:8: NUMBER_LIT 1
7:10: VAR_TYPE str
7:15: SAID called
7:22: STR_LIT "今有雞翁一，值錢五；雞母一，值錢三；雞雛三，值錢一。"
7:54: PRINT print
8:1: HERE_ARE i have
8:8: NUMBER_LIT 1
8:10: VAR_TYPE str
8:15: SAID called
8:22: STR_LIT "凡百錢買雞百隻，問雞翁、母、雛各幾何？"
8:47: PRINT print
10:1: HERE_IS_A has a
10:7: VAR_TYPE num
10:11: NUMBER_LIT 100
10:16: NAME_IT name it
10:24: IDENT '百'
11:1: HERE_IS_A has a
11:7: VAR_TYPE num
11:11: NUMBER_LIT 0
11:14: NAME_IT name it
11:22: IDENT '翁'
13:1: COMMENT NOTE
13:6: STR_LIT " 第一層迴圈：翁至多二十隻 "
14:1: WHILE_TRUE while true
14:13: IF if
14:16: IDENT '翁'
14:20: EXP_LOGIC >
14:22: NUMBER_LIT 20
14:25: TOPIC topic
14:31: BREAK break
14:37: END end
16:5: HERE_IS_A has a
16:11: VAR_TYPE num
16:15: NUMBER_LIT 0
16:18: NAME_IT name it
16:26: IDENT '母'
17:5: COMMENT NOTE
17:10: STR_LIT " 第二層迴圈：母至多三十三隻 "
18:5: WHILE_TRUE while true
18:17: IF if
18:20: IDENT '母'
18:24: EXP_LOGIC >
18:26: NUMBER_LIT 33
18:29: TOPIC topic
18:35: BREAK break
18:41: END end
20:9: COMMENT NOTE
20:14: STR_LIT " 雛 = 百 - 翁 - 母 "
21:9: EXP_MATH -
21:13: IDENT '百'
21:17: ->
21:20: IDENT '翁'
21:25: EXP_MATH -
21:29: ITS its
21:33: ->
21:36: IDENT '母'
21:41: NAME_IT name it
21:49: IDENT '雛'
23:9: COMMENT NOTE
23:14: STR_LIT " 驗證 雛 是否為三之倍數 (雛 % 3 == 0) "
24:9: EXP_MATH /
24:13: IDENT '雛'
24:17: ->
24:20: NUMBER_LIT 3
24:23: EXP_MATH_OP %
24:28: NAME_IT name it
24:36: IDENT '雛餘'
26:9: IF if
26:12: IDENT '雛餘'
26:17: EXP_LOGIC ==
26:20: NUMBER_LIT 0
26:22: TOPIC topic
27:13: COMMENT NOTE
27:18: STR_LIT " 總價 = 翁*5 + 母*3 + 雛/3 "
28:13: EXP_MATH *
28:17: IDENT '翁'
28:21: ->
28:24: NUMBER_LIT 5
28:27: NAME_IT name it
28:35: IDENT '翁價'
29:13: EXP_MATH *
29:17: IDENT '母'
29:21: ->
29:24: NUMBER_LIT 3
29:27: NAME_IT name it
29:35: IDENT '母價'
30:13: EXP_MATH /
30:17: IDENT '雛'
30:21: ->
30:24: NUMBER_LIT 3
30:27: NAME_IT name it
30:35: IDENT '雛價'
32:13: EXP_MATH +
32:17: IDENT '翁價'
32:22: ->
32:25: IDENT '母價'
32:31: EXP_MATH +
32:35: ITS its
32:39: ->
32:42: IDENT '雛價'
32:48: NAME_IT name it
32:56: IDENT '總價'
34:13: IF if
34:16: IDENT '總價'
34:21: EXP_LOGIC ==
34:24: IDENT '百'
34:28: TOPIC topic
35:17: COMMENT NOTE
35:22: STR_LIT " 採直接交錯列印文字與變數 "
36:17: HERE_ARE i have
36:24: NUMBER_LIT 7
36:26: VAR_TYPE str
36:31: SAID called
36:38: STR_LIT "得解：翁"
36:48: SAID called
36:55: IDENT '翁'
37:21: SAID called
37:28: STR_LIT "隻，母"
37:37: SAID called
37:44: IDENT '母'
38:21: SAID called
38:28: STR_LIT "隻，雛"
38:37: SAID called
38:44: IDENT '雛'
39:21: SAID called
39:28: STR_LIT "隻。"
39:36: PRINT print
40:13: END end
41:9: END end
43:9: EXP_MATH +
43:13: IDENT '母'
43:17: ->
43:20: NUMBER_LIT 1
43:23: PAST prev
43:28: IDENT '母'
43:32: TOPIC topic
43:39: SET set
43:43: ITS its
43:47: IS_THUS is thus
44:5: END end
46:5: EXP_MATH +
46:9: IDENT '翁'
46:13: ->
46:16: NUMBER_LIT 1
46:19: PAST prev
46:24: IDENT '翁'
46:28: TOPIC topic
46:35: SET set
46:39: ITS its
46:43: IS_THUS is thus
47:1: END end
